addDebtorNotice Method

Overview

This method will be used for adding an invoice detail and attachment.

Business Rule

  • Fields (import details, company details, accounts, owners, management, properties, contact, insurance, attachments) under request must be mandatory.
  • On the response, status after saving will be displayed.

Usage

  • This will be used on adding an invoice detail and attachment.
